the mistakes to be that serious.

84
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:47,730
So I wrote up this report.

85
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,940
I was going to give it to Mr. Zhang.

86
00:08:58,150 --> 00:08:59,340
Is what you wrote in here true?

87
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:01,940
Did you guys really
mess up the case back then?

88
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,220
It's pretty much confirmed.

89
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:11,420
Then why didn't you

90
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,220
hand it to Mr. Zhang?

91
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:14,530
I was going to.

92
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,220
I even had it in my hand the other day.

93
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,250
But then you knocked, went in,

94
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,730
and showed us Jiang Hongjun's video.

95
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,820
Then you just dragged me

96
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,460
into this team, no questions asked.

97
00:09:22,510 --> 00:09:23,940
I even tried to stop you. Remember?

98
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,370
I did. But you didn't listen.

99
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:26,770
So why didn't you hand it in
after I left?

100
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,060
I took a chance.

101
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:28,980
That's how people are.

102
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,490
Once that burst of courage is gone,

103
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:31,460
you start hoping for the best.

104
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,340
People all have that weakness.

105
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:38,340
I'm telling Mr. Zhang.

106
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,460
No, don't.

107
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,100
This is huge, I'm telling you,
Hong Liang.

108
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,370
Let's clear this up between us first.

109
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,650
Didn't I just ask you

110
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:45,460
