113
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:48,010
I...!

114
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:49,530
Don't!

115
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:54,730
No signal, huh?

116
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:06,940
Hong Liang, listen up.

117
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:08,370
I haven't read

118
00:10:09,030 --> 00:10:10,580
