119
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,060
I'm trying to ask you to help!

120
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,300
Help me figure this out.

121
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,420
What do you want me to do?

122
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,300
Hong Liang, you know me.

123
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:18,490
In my eyes, there's only
right and wrong,

124
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,650
no middle ground.

125
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,370
You're dragging me down with you!

126
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:22,770
For over a decade in this office,

127
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:23,580
I've never made a single friend!

128
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,770
I have no one to turn to!

129
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:25,820
I had to come to you!

130
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,460
I thought that

131
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:40,420
after doing this job for over 20 years,

132
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:42,890
I could walk away with a clean record.

133
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:45,300
Who'd have thought

134
00:10:47,510 --> 00:10:48,370
it would blow up like this?

135
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:50,820
Maybe I'll take off
the prosecutor's uniform

136
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,890
and end up in a prison jumpsuit.

137
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,060
The worst part is,

138
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:55,060
if I take the fall for this,

139
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,850
I can't stay in the Task Force.

140
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:58,820
Then what?

141
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,700
I won't be able to look into

142
00:11:00,790 --> 00:11:02,580
what I know or what I can follow.

143
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:04,650
And Qiao

144
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,580
would stay dead without any answers.

145
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:11,460
I won't be able to help
with the Wan Hai case

146
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,420
and all those things in Dongping.

147
00:11:15,870 --> 00:11:17,060
I'll have let too many people down.

148
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,060
It's a pity.

149
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:22,820
I can't accept it.

150
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:26,980
That's why

151
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,370
I'm giving this letter

152
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:31,890
to you today.

153
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,490
Once the Task Force wraps up its work,

154
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:40,100
feel free to do as you see fit.

155
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:41,730
Help me.

156
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:54,180
You're asking me
to make mistakes with you.

157
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:40,610
Chen Shenglong!

158
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,300
Chen Shenglong!

159
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:42,940
Mr. Wang.

160
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:45,890
You can just talk to me over the phone.

161
00:12:46,390 --> 00:12:47,100
Why come all the way here?

162
00:12:53,670 --> 00:12:55,220
After Wan Hai met his brother today,

163
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:56,980
