164
00:12:58,510 --> 00:12:59,700
Did you push him too hard?

165
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,700
Then he asked me

166
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:03,010
how to file an appeal.

167
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:06,130
Do you know what this means?

168
00:13:08,910 --> 00:13:09,530
I'm telling you,

169
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,100
if that day really comes,

170
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,340
none of you can walk away!

171
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,460
I came here

172
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,610
to give you a heads-up.

173
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,250
What should we do about this?

174
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,010
Think about it.

175
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:34,650
Think about it!

176
00:13:45,870 --> 00:13:47,250
That thing I asked you
to take care of before...?

177
00:13:49,030 --> 00:13:49,530
It's done.

178
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,300
US dollar account.

179
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,610
New passport.

180
00:13:59,790 --> 00:14:00,420
Looks pretty solid.

181
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,980
We are professional.

182
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,060
Mr. Wang.

183
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,700
I need you

184
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,340
to keep a close eye on it.

185
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:10,940
I'm counting on you.

186
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:11,530
Sure,

187
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,770
I'll keep watching.

188
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:17,060
But you all,

189
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,610
