203
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:47,300
So,

204
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:48,490
get your head straight.

205
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,340
Don't keep pushing it,

206
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,460
and don't push your luck!

207
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,180
If this blows up,
none of us walks away clean.

208
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,250
What do you mean?

209
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:02,700
Who do you think you're yelling at?

210
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,650
Can't you talk nicely?

211
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,250
What now?

212
00:15:06,630 --> 00:15:07,980
You're still breathing here because of me!

213
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:10,890
Wang Dayou,
why your name is now Xiong Lei?

214
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:11,770
Don't you remember?

215
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,420
I changed my name
from Wang Dayou to Xiong Lei.

216
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:16,980
Did you do it for nothing?

217
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,250
Did you not get paid?

218
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:19,100
Did you call in any favors?

219
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:19,610
I'm telling you...

220
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:20,010
What?

221
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:21,580
I don't even want to look at you.

222
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,530
Cut it out!

223
00:15:22,630 --> 00:15:23,890
Here's your chance, come on, now.

224
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:24,300
What?

225
00:15:24,390 --> 00:15:24,940
Hit me, come on!

226
00:15:25,270 --> 00:15:25,980
Listen up.

227
00:15:26,270 --> 00:15:27,420
A new ID card

228
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:28,420
doesn't mean you're someone now.

229
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,700
Without me, you'd be dead already!

230
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:31,730
My power plant is short on garbage.

231
00:15:32,550 --> 00:15:33,770
You wanna be in it?

232
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,340
Do you wanna die?

233
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:11,370
Everyone, take a look.

234
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,700
This is the first arrest operation
carried out by our Task Force

235
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,180
since its establishment.

236
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:17,890
Let's have Mr. Hong

237
00:16:17,910 --> 00:16:18,730
give us a quick briefing.

238
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:23,460
Alright,

239
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,610
let me walk you through
the basic situation.

240
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,010
After several days of surveillance,

241
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,650
we found that the target

242
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:34,490
follows a fairly regular routine.

243
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:35,890
Especially on weekdays.

244
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:36,940
Every morning

245
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,980
between 7:10 and 7:15,

246
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,940
he leaves to drop his kid off at school.

247
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:43,100
It takes 20 minutes

248
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:45,100
from his home to the school.

249
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:46,700
Because parking is not allowed
at the school gate,

250
00:16:46,870 --> 00:16:48,010
he usually parks his car

251
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:50,010
on the roadside diagonally
across from the school

252
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,060
and then walks the kid over.

253
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:54,420
About five minutes later,
he returns to his car

254
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,650
and drives to work.

255
00:16:58,550 --> 00:16:59,890
Now I'll go over

256
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:03,060
the arrest plan jointly formulated

257
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,220
by Mr. Hong and Captain Hu Zhinan.

258
00:17:04,510 --> 00:17:05,010
First,

259
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,140
Zhang and I

260
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:08,180
will keep watching
in the underground garage

261
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,220
of the target's residence.

262
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:10,770
As soon as the target leaves,

263
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,010
we'll head upstairs immediately.

264
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:13,660
Captain Hu Zhinan

265
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:14,420
will lead a team

266
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,220
to set up surveillance
near the school gate,

267
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:17,810
waiting for the right moment
to make the arrest.

268
00:17:19,030 --> 00:17:20,010
I'll be in charge on-site.

269
00:17:20,830 --> 00:17:21,940
I'm on Channel 1.

270
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:24,140
Please switch your walkie-talkies
to Frequency 11.

271
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,290
If there are no questions,
let's move out.

272
00:17:49,120 --> 00:17:51,560
[Block 2]

273
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:52,010
Ate enough?

274
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:52,810
Yes.

275
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:54,900
Target spotted.

276
00:18:06,070 --> 00:18:06,730
Vehicle departing.

277
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:18,620
Go.

278
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:28,380
You are?

279
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,530
We're from the Procuratorate.

280
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:30,600
[Search Warrant]
Conducting a lawful search

281
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,980
of Jiang Hongjun's residence.

282
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,810
What happened

283
00:18:34,510 --> 00:18:35,380
to my husband?

284
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:36,860
Thank you.

