291
00:19:27,030 --> 00:19:27,730
Thought so.

292
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:32,810
Remember, healthy lunch.

293
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:35,290
Ning.

294
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:37,530
Give Daddy a kiss.

295
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:44,620
