306
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:57,420
Nothing.

307
00:20:59,110 --> 00:20:59,660
No...

308
00:21:06,550 --> 00:21:07,010
Let's pull out.

309
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:10,860
Sorry for the disturbance.

310
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,810
Who lives next door?

311
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:54,250
Who lives next door?

312
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:55,620
I'm asking you.

313
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:00,700
My next door

314
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:03,330
is Jiang's brother's place,

315
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,620
but he's abroad.

316
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:06,860
No one's lived there for a long time.

317
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:07,660
Open the door.

318
00:23:17,960 --> 00:23:18,420
Zhang.

319
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:19,700
Zhang!

320
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:08,330
After sending the email

321
00:24:08,350 --> 00:24:09,460
to Ms. Zheng from this computer,

322
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:10,900
Wan Chao left the Internet café,

323
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:12,730
walked through this alley,

324
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,380
and disappeared.

325
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:16,530
The area's a mess,

326
00:24:16,750 --> 00:24:18,380
no good surveillance.

327
00:24:19,270 --> 00:24:20,530
So we lost the trail after that.

328
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,490
Our team was on-site quickly

329
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:23,810
but

330
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,660
has found no leads.

331
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:29,180
We've already deployed
plainclothes officers in Dongping

332
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,010
to keep looking for him.

333
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:32,940
Thank you.

334
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,180
Mr. Song, I know

335
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:37,010
the police officers are
under a heavy workload.

336
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:38,660
