341
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:49,490
When our Guidance Group
went to Dongping earlier,

342
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:50,490
we found some leads

343
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:53,460
but couldn't follow up
due to interference.

344
00:24:54,310 --> 00:24:55,730
I hope you can help me

345
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:57,090
investigate them thoroughly.

346
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:58,010
Their backgrounds,

347
00:24:58,440 --> 00:24:59,220
social connections,

348
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:01,660
communications, and bank statements.

349
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:03,010
Okay.

350
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:04,010
Meanwhile,

351
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,420
we still have to find Wan Chao
as soon as possible.

352
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:07,810
Please.

353
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:09,250
No problem.

354
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,090
Buying cigarettes?

355
00:25:23,750 --> 00:25:24,940
