Do you have a phone?

356
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:25,730
Yeah, inside.

357
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:37,220
Who's that?

358
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,220
Uncle,

359
00:25:38,830 --> 00:25:39,620
it's me,

360
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:40,490
Chao?

361
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:42,050
Where are you?

362
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,730
I can't get out.

363
00:25:43,790 --> 00:25:45,250
I'm still in Dongping.

364
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:47,250
The cops have my face
on wanted posters

365
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,530
everywhere.

366
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:51,420
And someone else is after me too.

367
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:54,460
I'm hiding in that old factory,

368
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:55,770
the bathhouse, remember?

369
00:25:55,790 --> 00:25:56,620
I stay there now.

370
00:25:56,830 --> 00:25:58,660
Uncle, come quickly.

371
00:25:58,920 --> 00:25:59,900
I'm starving.

372
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:00,900
Okay, I see.

373
00:26:01,550 --> 00:26:02,290
Listen,

374
00:26:02,590 --> 00:26:03,250
don't go anywhere,

375
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:04,220
