376
00:26:04,310 --> 00:26:04,940
I'm coming to you.

377
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:07,090
Okay, I'll wait for you there.

378
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,290
Okay...

379
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,160
[Dongping Public Security Bureau]

380
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:15,090
Mr. Sun.

381
00:26:38,200 --> 00:26:38,490
Hello?

382
00:26:38,510 --> 00:26:39,090
Mr. Sun.

383
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:41,770
This morning, a whole team
came and searched my house.

384
00:26:42,270 --> 00:26:42,810
And

385
00:26:43,510 --> 00:26:46,570
they found cash at home.

386
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:49,700
That's ridiculous.

387
00:26:50,030 --> 00:26:51,420
Why would you keep cash at home?

388
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:53,860
Did they show any certificates?

389
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:56,090
They did, but

390
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:57,940
I was so scared.

391
00:26:58,680 --> 00:26:59,490
I don't remember

392
00:26:59,510 --> 00:27:01,330
anything they said.

393
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,290
After they left,

394
00:27:02,310 --> 00:27:04,050
I tried to call Jiang

395
00:27:04,750 --> 00:27:05,860
but couldn't reach him.

396
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,460
I didn't know what to do,

397
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,900
so I called you.

398
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:10,180
Mr. Sun.

399
00:27:10,590 --> 00:27:12,460
You must save Jiang.

400
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:13,490
Okay, I got it.

401
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:14,810
Wait for my update.

402
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:16,660
And keep your mouth shut,

403
00:27:16,680 --> 00:27:17,330
don't tell anybody anything.

404
00:27:26,790 --> 00:27:27,570
Where is this?

405
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:28,570
Let me go!

406
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,140
Where is this?

407
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:52,050
Turn to the side.

408
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:55,770
Chao, it's me.

409
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:57,900
Chao.

410
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:01,380
Chao.

411
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:04,380
Chao.

412
00:29:21,070 --> 00:29:21,620
Chao.

413
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:25,860
Chao.

414
00:30:05,550 --> 00:30:06,140
Uncle.

415
00:30:08,590 --> 00:30:10,330
Where have you been?

416
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:13,620
Do you know how much trouble
you got into?

417
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:24,530
I haven't eaten for two days.

418
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:25,330
It hurts.

419
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:27,660
Hungry?

420
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,460
I brought you food.

421
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:33,140
Don't cry.

422
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:34,140
It's okay now.

423
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,700
So miserable...

424
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:37,530
Here, drink some water first.

425
00:30:37,550 --> 00:30:39,730
No. I want food.

426
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:41,380
What you wanna eat? Take a look.

427
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:44,620
There's sausage.

428
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:47,380
Sausage.

429
00:30:49,270 --> 00:30:50,530
Thank God I found you.

430
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:55,530
Chao.

431
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:57,530
This place is not good.

432
00:30:58,590 --> 00:30:59,860
Not safe enough.

433
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:02,090
We have to move to another place.

434
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:05,420
They've been looking for you
all over the past two days.

435
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:09,940
Maybe they'll come here soon.

436
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,330
They?

437
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:19,010
Who are they?

438
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:21,250
Who?

439
00:31:24,590 --> 00:31:26,010
Police, who else?

440
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:27,730
