444
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:36,460
If they catch you, it's over.

445
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:37,620
Listen to me.

446
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:38,770
Come with me.

447
00:31:39,550 --> 00:31:40,420
- Hurry.
- Where are we going?

448
00:31:40,510 --> 00:31:41,090
The mine.

449
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,570
What? Isn't that sealed too?

450
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:46,490
What's the difference?

451
00:31:46,590 --> 00:31:47,730
The mine is more dangerous than here.

452
00:31:47,830 --> 00:31:49,490
The more dangerous the place,
the safer it actually is.

453
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:51,420
Hiding in plain sight.
Ever heard of it, kid?

454
00:31:55,030 --> 00:31:55,530
Go!

455
00:32:06,270 --> 00:32:07,250
What now?

456
00:32:08,070 --> 00:32:08,570
Uncle.

457
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:11,980
I owe you an apology.

458
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,620
I shouldn't have gone mining secretly.

459
00:32:15,070 --> 00:32:16,090
