before we started.

464
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,530
No way anything could've gone wrong.

465
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:27,980
If someone did this to us,

466
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:31,460
who would that be, Uncle?
Who did we offend?

467
00:32:31,790 --> 00:32:32,460
Chao...

468
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:34,290
Nobody did it to us.

469
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:35,770
We didn't offend anyone.

470
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:38,180
Remember, this was an accident.

471
00:32:38,350 --> 00:32:39,420
Just an accident.

472
00:32:40,590 --> 00:32:41,330
Don't think about anything.

473
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,220
As long as you're safe,

474
00:32:43,350 --> 00:32:44,570
your father didn't go to jail for nothing.

475
00:32:44,750 --> 00:32:45,220
Understand?

476
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,290
Keeping you alive is
all that matters now.

477
00:32:46,510 --> 00:32:47,460
Keep who alive?

478
00:32:47,960 --> 00:32:48,700
Keep me alive?

479
00:32:49,070 --> 00:32:50,660
Who's trying to kill me?

480
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:54,250
Uncle.

481
00:32:55,510 --> 00:32:56,420
I'm begging you.

482
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:58,180
If you know something, tell me!

483
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,620
I don't know anything!

484
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:02,770
All I know now is
nothing can happen to you.

485
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:04,250
Nothing can happen to you!

486
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:06,050
Chao,

487
00:33:06,550 --> 00:33:07,620
can you listen to me?

488
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:09,460
I'd never hurt you.

489
00:33:10,030 --> 00:33:10,460
Go.

490
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:12,660
Wait...

491
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:50,180
Where is this?

492
00:33:50,270 --> 00:33:50,730
Be quiet.

493
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:51,490
Let go of me.

494
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:52,940
Turn around.

495
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:53,490
Do not move.

496
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:56,010
Who's in charge here?

497
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:57,380
What's the meaning of this?

498
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,250
We're on the same side.

499
00:34:03,750 --> 00:34:04,220
Hong Liang!

500
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:05,250
Hong Liang!

501
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:05,940
Have you got it?

502
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:06,730
Yes.

503
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:10,340
How much?

504
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:11,900
3.23 million in cash and 28 gold bars.

505
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:14,490
I'll send it to Luo.

506
00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:15,260
Okay.

507
00:34:17,510 --> 00:34:18,490
Bring your superior here.

508
00:34:20,510 --> 00:34:21,260
Where is he?

509
00:34:22,630 --> 00:34:23,340
Anyone here?

510
00:34:24,230 --> 00:34:25,780
You arrested me and just leave me here?

511
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:34,490
Sorry, I'm late.

512
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:42,570
Shall we start?

513
00:34:44,230 --> 00:34:44,610
Name?

514
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:49,530
Name?

515
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:55,130
Jiang Hongjun, can't you hear me?

516
00:34:55,230 --> 00:34:56,300
