523
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:09,300
What's this, kid?

524
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:10,490
You think you can interrogate me?

525
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:14,260
When I was doing interrogations,
you were still in diapers.

526
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:16,260
Right.

527
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:17,690
I'm young.

528
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:19,900
But Haidong Provincial Procuratorate
is not.

529
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:23,340
Hong Liang.

530
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:24,980
You say it.

531
00:35:27,590 --> 00:35:29,940
Show the young one some respect.

532
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:32,900
Let him get some practice.

533
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:41,980
Jiang Hongjun.

534
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:44,860
42 years old.

535
00:35:45,190 --> 00:35:46,340
Ethnicity, Han.

536
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:49,340
Place of origin,
Xinhua District, Dongping City.

537
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,090
Position and occupation,

538
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:52,940
Captain
of the Criminal Investigation Unit,

539
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:54,380
Dongping Development Zone sub-bureau.

540
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:55,610
Married.

541
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:57,740
My wife is a full-time housewife.

542
00:35:58,030 --> 00:35:59,650
I have a daughter who is ten years old

543
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:00,740
