544
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:01,650
Anything missing?

545
00:36:08,710 --> 00:36:10,260
Shouldn't you show me
a little respect too?

546
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:13,610
What's with all these restraints?

547
00:36:14,150 --> 00:36:15,940
If you don't get something
clear out of me today,

548
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:16,380
Hong Liang,

549
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:18,940
once I get out,
you must take full responsibility.

550
00:36:19,510 --> 00:36:21,050
How can I handle
that kind of responsibility?

551
00:36:21,670 --> 00:36:22,420
You guys

552
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,420
