553
00:36:24,510 --> 00:36:26,420
He's from the political-legal system.

554
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,570
He won't hurt you.

555
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:28,490
Come on, hurry.

556
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,820
