Stand up...

566
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,210
Stretch a bit.

567
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,690
Since getting in your car,

568
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:02,980
I've counted about

569
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:04,900
28 intersections.

570
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,940
I'm getting old

571
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:08,740
and can't remember that well.

572
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,380
Did you

573
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:11,780
turn left or right

574
00:37:12,550 --> 00:37:13,010
at the 12th intersection…?

575
00:37:13,030 --> 00:37:13,820
What are you shooting?

